meta.description: Command-line client for Papertrail hosted log management service.
meta.long_description: Command-line client for Papertrail hosted log management service. Tails and searches app server logs and system syslog. Supports Boolean search and works with grep and pipe output (Unix).
meta.name: ruby-papertrail
